name: DorkDiariesTrivia
0:
”Alexa, open Dork Diaries Trivia”
”Alexa, start Dork Diaries Trivia”
”Repeat”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dork diaries trivia
des:
There are 5 questions in every game. On every question there are 3 answers. Select one which you think is correct.
If you need to hear the question again, just say," Repeat.” At the end of the game you will hear your score. You can play this game more than once because some of the questions and answers will be different.
I really enjoyed creating this Dork Diaries Trivia game and I hope you will enjoy it too!
To start a game, just say," Alexa, open Dork Diaries Trivia." 
If you want to hear the question again, say, "Repeat." If you don't want to play anymore, just say," Alexa, Stop."
Have fun!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
